@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oiruaz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.55 + tmp + 0.71)))
    v1 = (v2 + ((tmp + 0.70 * v2 + 0.50) - 0.12))
    v0 = ((v2 * 0.42) / ((v0 + 0.69 + tmp + 0.65) + tmp))
    tmp = 0.81
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = 0.44
    v2 = wp.abs(0.63)
    data[tid] = v0
